{"article_id":"Vwq4y0QwKDSSeM2x","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Confronted with the durable phenomenon","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"known as Donald Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"the leading tried a new tack Tuesday night :","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"ignore him .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Trump didn ' t go anywhere , of course .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Attacks did flow in from candidates","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"who found themselves farther from center stage than ever","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"-- including , notably , Jeb Bush .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"But it ' s as if his front-running status is so familiar","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that his rivals for the most part chose not to fight him ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"as the race settles into its lanes .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"At a tense time in the nation , attention turned to once familiar","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"-- even old-school --","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"arguments inside the Republican Party .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"A scattered debate","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that focused almost exclusively on foreign policy and national security","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"revealed tension between the GOP ' s hawkish and libertarian strains , its Senate and gubernatorial leaders , and two first-term senators","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"who may well be the last Republican candidates standing .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The most tense exchanges pitted Ted Cruz against Marco Rubio , the onetime allies","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"who now see themselves as each other ' s most serious rival .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Rubio attacked Cruz","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"for supporting an end to surveillance programs and limiting defense spending ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"while Cruz hit Rubio hard over immigration .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"\" We are now at a time","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"where we need more tools , not less tools , \"","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"Rubio said .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Later , he added :","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"\" You can ' t carpet-bomb ISIS","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"if you don ' t have planes and bombs","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"to attack them with . \"","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"Cruz accused Rubio of distorting his record , and","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"-- a harsher charge --","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"empowering the Obama administration ' s mission .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"\" One of the problems with Marco 's foreign policy is he is far too often supported Hillary Clinton and Barack Obama undermining governments in the Middle East","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that have helped radical Islamic terrorists , \"","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Cruz said .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"It left Chris Christie open to argue a basic point","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"-- that the fights on stage probably weren ' t registering with voters","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"who are jittery in the wake of world and national events .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" Let 's talk about how we do this","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and not which bill","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"which these guys like more .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"People do n't care about that , \"","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Christie said .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"The anti-Trump charge was left mostly to Bush ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"whose migration away from center stage has been accompanied by a desire","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"to fight with the man","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"who still occupies it .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Bush attacked Trump for a lack of \" seriousness , \"","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"noting snidely at one point","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that he was giving him \" a bit of your own medicine . \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" Donald is great at the one-liners .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"But he ' s a chaos candidate .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"And he ' d be a chaos president , \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Bush said , in a line","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"worked up sufficiently in advance","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"so that his campaign had a Website with that label","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"ready to go .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Trump brushed the attacks aside ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"taunting Bush over his poll numbers and with now-familiar rejoinders .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" I know","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"you ' re trying to build up your energy , Jeb ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"but it ' s not working , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"\" You started off over here","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"and moving over further and further , \"","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Trump said later ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"referring to Bush ' s position on the stage .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" Pretty soon you ' re gon na be off the end . \"","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"With voting drawing near ,","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"the candidates are choosing the battles","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"that work for them .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Cruz and Rubio will claw at each other ' s records ;","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Christie , John Kasich , and Carly Fiorina will post up against the candidates","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"who work in Washington ;","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Bush is now positioning himself as the main anti-Trump force in the race .","depth":3},{"id":76,"text":"The last Republican debate of the year left the GOP","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"where it ' s been at the start of this wild , six-month run .","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"Trump may fade ,","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"but it looks increasingly likely that it won ' t be what the other candidates say about him","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"that makes it happen .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Toward the end of the debate , Trump even felt generous toward Cruz","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"-- now his closest rival in Iowa , and perhaps nationally .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"\" He has a wonderful temperament .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"He ' s just fine -","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"don ' t worry about it , \"","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"\" You better not attack . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":175,"left":156,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":98,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":91,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":89,"right":90,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":96,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":93,"right":95,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":5,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":8,"right":94,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":94,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":130,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":104,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":100,"right":103,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":101,"right":102,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":121,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"par